INSERT INTO `answers` VALUES (88,1,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>浮点数无法精确存储。<br>\n这个不是python 的问题，所有基于二进制的浮点数都会有这个问题，原因在于大部分浮点数转换为二进制后都是无限循环小数，而浮点数不可能用无限大的内存来储存，所以会有舍入的误差。<br>\n可以参考Python中的decimal模块。<br><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/bitcarmanlee/article/details/51179572\">http://blog.csdn.net/bitcarmanlee/article/details/51179572</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:01','2017-02-12 12:11:01'),(89,2,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>serializeArray() 方法通过序列化表单值来创建对象数组（名称和值）。而你正确的格式是JSON对象不是数组呢。<br>\n如果你要用serializeArray()的话，后台的PHP应该按JSON数组方式处理请求参数才对呢。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:01','2017-02-12 12:11:01'),(90,3,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>设置一个最小宽度，这样无论怎样都不会缩小到小于这个宽度，标题也不会掉下来<br>\nmix-width: <br>\n设置字体大小随浏览器宽度变化而变化。<br>\n建议用media 查询，把最小宽度和字体大小自适应都加上</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:01','2017-02-12 12:11:01'),(91,3,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>用div把他括起来 然后div自适应一下试试</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:01','2017-02-12 12:11:01'),(92,4,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/qingyuanluofeng/article/details/54933869\">http://blog.csdn.net/qingyuanluofeng/article/details/54933869</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:01','2017-02-12 12:11:01'),(93,5,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>应该是只执行这行代码吧，代码执行的时候回一个item一个item的依次往下去找，直到找到符合条件的item去加载。<br>\n找到符合条件的item后，后面的item就不执行了。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(94,5,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>而且你这样写会报错的吧，item必须有个tag属性，也就是说第一个item必须有drawable。我自己试了试linearLayout是可以的。<br>\n如果没有找到符合条件的item就没有背景。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(95,6,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>通过FileListBox1控件的方法. 如下: 读取: img1.Picture.LoadFromFile (FileListBox1.FileName ); 和 遍历FileListBox1.ItemIndex:=FileListBox1.ItemIndex+1; </p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(96,6,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>1 获取路径下图片，并存放到数组中。<br>\n2.设置初始位置<br>\n３.在Timage控件点击事件中：</p>\n\n<pre><code>显示数组下一个位置对应的图片；\n    当前位置+1\n    判断当前位置，如果大于数组长度\n    当前位置 = 初始位置。\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(97,7,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>chdir改变的是程序自己的目录，不会影响你shell</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(98,8,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>dotNET_Reactor混淆下</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(99,8,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/xiaohan2826/article/details/8995349\">http://blog.csdn.net/xiaohan2826/article/details/8995349</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(100,8,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>用sixxpack来加壳</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(101,9,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>我已经知道了。。。原来是指已经运行了2次出来的结果</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(102,10,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>clean一下，对着依赖中有没有这个jar包，有可能是没有这个版本的jar</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(103,10,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>用的是intellij idea</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(104,10,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>如果仅仅是下边有红线，而项目启动运行正常的话，可以先在pom文件中把它删掉，保存后，再Ctrl+Z撤销回来，再进行保存，应该就可以了。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(105,10,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>clean一下试试。。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(106,10,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>可能是包冲突，或者pom.xml中写得包的依赖不对</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(107,10,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>这个影响项目运行吗？jar包冲突了吧。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:02','2017-02-12 12:11:02'),(108,11,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>ajax用了跨域的请求，所以出错，后来我把请求放在服务器端完成，就可以了，只是双引号要转义一下。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:03','2017-02-12 12:11:03'),(109,12,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>总共多少条<br>\nSELECT COUNT(*) FROM table1 + SELECT COUNT(*) FROM table2<br>\n分别查询<br>\n(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM table1) union (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM table2)<br>\n假设一个是10，一个是20<br>\n第一个返回30<br>\n第二个返回<br>\n10<br>\n20</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:03','2017-02-12 12:11:03'),(110,13,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>在wm_size里发一个wm_paint强制客户区重画。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(111,13,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>解决了，原来是我没有在paint结束时删除位图DC</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(112,14,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>@战在春秋: </p>\n\n<p>SET NOCOUNT ON<br>\nSELECT<br>\n    *<br>\nFROM<br>\n    [dbo].[ZS_delphi]<br>\nFOR XML AUTO, ELEMENTS, ROOT(\'xml\')<br>\n测试结果: <a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486657287_983352.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486657287_983352.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<p>sqlcmd -S . -d AzureDemo50 -E -s, -W -i ZS_delphi.sql | findstr /V /C:\"-\" /B &gt; ExcelTest.csv<br>\n测试结果: 通不过.</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(113,14,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.excel-sql-server.com/sql-server-export-to-excel-using-bcp-sqlcmd-csv.htm\">借助SQLCMD或者BCP</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(114,14,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>可能你没注意，那篇链接文章的底部有源文件zip格式的下载，里面有详细步骤</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(115,15,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <pre><code> package com.zzk.ceshi;\n\nimport java.io.BufferedReader;\nimport java.io.FileWriter;\nimport java.io.InputStreamReader;\nimport java.io.PrintWriter;\nimport java.net.HttpURLConnection;\nimport java.net.URL;\nimport java.util.regex.Matcher;\nimport java.util.regex.Pattern;\n\npublic class GetMail {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n         String regex=\"\\\\b[A-Za-z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+\\\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,}\\\\b\";\n//          String s=\"\";\n            StringBuilder s = new StringBuilder(\"\");\n            String line=null;\n            try{\n            URL url=new URL(\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4232750852\");\n            HttpURLConnection uc=(HttpURLConnection)url.openConnection();\n            BufferedReader br=new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(uc.getInputStream()));\n            PrintWriter pw=new PrintWriter(new FileWriter(\"d:\\\\data.txt\"),true);\n            while((line=br.readLine())!=null){\n                //s=s+line;//如果s用StringBuilder或者StringBuffer代替（s=null)则抛出  NullPointerException\n                s.append(line);\n            }\n            Pattern p=Pattern.compile(regex);\n            Matcher m=p.matcher(s);\n            while(m.find()){\n                pw.println(m.group());\n            }\n            pw.close();\n            }catch(Exception e){\n                e.printStackTrace();\n            }\n        }\n\n\n}\n\n\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486691011_698851.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486691011_698851.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(116,15,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>```package com.zzk.ceshi;</p>\n\n<p>import java.io.BufferedReader;<br>\nimport java.io.FileWriter;<br>\nimport java.io.InputStreamReader;<br>\nimport java.io.PrintWriter;<br>\nimport java.net.HttpURLConnection;<br>\nimport java.net.URL;<br>\nimport java.util.regex.Matcher;<br>\nimport java.util.regex.Pattern;</p>\n\n<p>public class GetMail {</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String[] args) {\n     String regex=\"\\\\b[A-Za-z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+\\\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,}\\\\b\";\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>//          String s=\"\";<br>\n            StringBuilder s = new StringBuilder(\"\");<br>\n            String line=null;<br>\n            try{<br>\n            URL url=new URL(\"<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4232750852%22\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4232750852\"</a>);<br>\n            HttpURLConnection uc=(HttpURLConnection)url.openConnection();<br>\n            BufferedReader br=new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(uc.getInputStream()));<br>\n            PrintWriter pw=new PrintWriter(new FileWriter(\"d:\\data.txt\"),true);<br>\n            while((line=br.readLine())!=null){<br>\n                //s=s+line;//如果s用StringBuilder或者StringBuffer代替（s=null)则抛出  NullPointerException<br>\n                s.append(line);<br>\n            }<br>\n            Pattern p=Pattern.compile(regex);<br>\n            Matcher m=p.matcher(s);<br>\n            while(m.find()){<br>\n                pw.println(m.group());<br>\n            }<br>\n            pw.close();<br>\n            }catch(Exception e){<br>\n                e.printStackTrace();<br>\n            }<br>\n        }</p>\n\n<p>}</p>\n\n<pre><code>换成StringBuilder怎么会有问题呢？\n![图片说明](http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486691058_638309.png)\n\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(117,15,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>首先，原因很简单：你的正则错误了，另外，用StringBuffer没有问题，只是你用的不对。修正代码如下：</p>\n\n<pre><code> public static void main(String[] args) {\n        String regex=\"\\\\w+([-+.]\\\\w+)*@\\\\w+([-.]\\\\w+)*\\\\.\\\\w+([-.]\\\\w+)*\";\n        String line=null;\n        try{\n        URL url=new URL(\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4232750852\");\n        HttpURLConnection uc=(HttpURLConnection)url.openConnection();\n        BufferedReader br=new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(uc.getInputStream()));\n        PrintWriter pw=new PrintWriter(new FileWriter(\"d:\\\\data.txt\"),true);\n        StringBuffer buffer = new StringBuffer();\n        while((line=br.readLine())!=null){\n            buffer.append(line);\n        }\n\n        String s = buffer.toString();\n        Pattern p=Pattern.compile(regex);\n        Matcher m=p.matcher(s);\n        while(m.find()){\n            pw.println(m.group());\n        }\n        pw.close();\n        }catch(Exception e){\n            e.printStackTrace();\n        }\n    }\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>运行看看，data.txt里面就有邮箱信息啦。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(118,15,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>public class Test {<br>\n    public static void main(String[] args) {<br>\n//      String regex = \"[a-zA-Z_0-9]+@(\\.[a-zA-Z_0-9]{2,3})+\";<br>\n        String regex =\"[a-zA-Z0-9]{5,13}+@+[a-zA-Z0-9]{2,5}\";<br>\n        StringBuffer sb=new StringBuffer();<br>\n        String path=\"d:/data.txt\";<br>\n        String line = null;<br>\n        try {<br>\n            URL url = new URL(\"<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4232750852%22\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4232750852\"</a>);<br>\n            HttpURLConnection uc = (HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection();<br>\n            BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(uc.getInputStream()));<br>\n            File file=new File(path);<br>\n            if(!(file.exists())){<br>\n                file.createNewFile();<br>\n            }<br>\n            PrintWriter pw = new PrintWriter(new FileWriter(path),true);<br>\n            while ((line = br.readLine()) != null) {<br>\n                sb.append(line+\"\\n\");// 如果s用StringBuilder或者StringBuffer代替（s=null)则抛出<br>\n                                // NullPointerException<br>\n            }<br>\n            Pattern p = Pattern.compile(regex);<br>\n            Matcher m = p.matcher(sb);<br>\n            while (m.find()) {<br>\n                pw.println(m.group());<br>\n            }<br>\n            pw.close();<br>\n        } catch (Exception e) {<br>\n            e.printStackTrace();<br>\n        }<br>\n    }<br>\n}</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:04','2017-02-12 12:11:04'),(119,16,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>请参考这个 <a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/qieqing/articles/1224085.html\">http://www.cnblogs.com/qieqing/articles/1224085.html</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(120,16,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://www.w3dev.cn/article/20130409/css-selector-Priority.aspx\">CSS选择器优先级</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(121,16,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>css优先也就是权重。一般来说id权重 100，css权重10，元素权重1，内嵌权重1000，优先级最大的就是在元素后面添加!important.基本属于无敌的存在<a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486713194_188962.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201702/10/1486713194_188962.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(122,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>首先你要想好如何去定义一个数据类型为数组的数组<br>\nint[] i 定义一个int的一维数组， <br>\nint[][]  i定义二维数组，分开看就可以理解为定义一个一维的数据元素为数组的数组。i[n]就是一维数组<br>\n现在再会过头来看你的需要，定义一个数据类型是数组的一维数组是不是等同于定义了一个二维数组<br>\n实际上就是定义的二维数组</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(123,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>二维数组，可以理解为是一种“特殊”的一维数组，它的每个数组空间中保存的是一个一维数组。其它高维也类似。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(124,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>对。就是一个二维数组。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(125,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>一维 int[] i<br>\n二维int[][] i</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(126,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>数组中的元素为另一个数组的首地址</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(127,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>是的，是一个二维数组，</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(128,17,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>是的。例如：int[][] arrays = new int[3][]<br>\narrays[i] = new int[strArray.length]</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(129,18,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>已经解决：<br>\nExt.getCmp(\"certificationfaillog\").close();<br>\ngrid.getStore().reload();</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(130,19,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>缓冲动画另外用css或者js之类的写，进页面执行</p>\n\n<p>xx.oncanplaythrough=function(){<br>\n    缓冲动画隐藏<br>\n    xx.play();<br>\n    //部分OEM会卡在99%，可以setTimeout强制play，时间看你素材大小和网络状况<br>\n}</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(131,19,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>preload=\"auto\"</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(132,19,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>可以这样考虑一下：先将视频的地址设置为空，在页面加载完成事件里先将poster设置为缓冲的gif图，并动态的将视频地址赋值给video标签。<br>\n在视频加载完成后将poster属性设置为空。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(133,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>是的，转换为字节数组了。<br>\nString转换为byte数组的过程，实际上就是对字符串进行编码转换的过程。getBytes()可以带参数的，比如\"utf8\"、\"gbk\"一类的，用来指定对字符串进行编码的时候使用的编码格式。不指定的话， 会使用操作系统默认的编码格式进行转换</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(134,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>String的getBytes()方法是得到一个系统默认的编码格式的字节数组。将一个String类型的字符串中包含的字符转换成byte类型并且存入一个byte[]数组中。在java中的所有数据底层都是字节，字节数据可以存入到byte数组。存储字符数据时（字符串就是字符数据），会先进行查表，然后将查询的结果写入设备，读取时也是先查表，把查到的内容打印到显示设备上，getBytes()是使用默认的字符集进行转换，getBytes(“utf-8”)是使用UTF-8编码表进行转换。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(135,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>后面那个for 只是为了打印bys 数组中的每一个值</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(136,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>for输出数组的值啊，，，，遇到代码，，可以用ide运行试试</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(137,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>循环是输出每个字节 直接输出数组名是 bys【0】的存储地址</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(138,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>for循环只是为了打印bys数组中每一值</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(139,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>for循环是为了遍历数组中的每一个值，如果不加for循环直接打印数组，就会打印出该数组的内存地址。除非你重写tostring()方法</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(140,20,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>String的getBytes()方法是返回得到一个系统默认的编码格式的字节数组<br>\n默认的是按照UTF-8编码表对String字符进行编码并返回字节数组。这个方法在io和网络编程中使用频繁。常常会将字符流转换成字节流，方便操作。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(141,21,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>对数据挖掘和机器学习懂一点。对人脸识别不熟悉，不过自己YY了一下<br>\n答案如下：<br>\n看你的用途是什么。<br>\n如果要识别具体的人，在添加新的人脸肯定是要训练的，至于是否将以前的数据合在一起重新训练，你可以选择这样，<br>\n当然你也可以不选择这么做。你应该听说过串联多个子BP构成一个系统。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:05','2017-02-12 12:11:05'),(142,22,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>需要用到ajax。。input blur后发送输入的内容到服务器端验证，这里有个demo，原理差不多，服务器端不是jsp的，自己改成jsp就行了，输出