nt-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/OceanEyes/archive/2012/02/04/ACM2098.html\">http://www.cnblogs.com/OceanEyes/archive/2012/02/04/ACM2098.html</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:46','2017-02-12 12:11:46'),(706,258,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>#include <br>\nconst int maxn = 10005;<br>\nint is_prime[maxn];<br>\nint main(){<br>\n    for(int i=0; i&lt;maxn; i++)<br>\n        is_prime[i] = 1;<br>\n    is_prime[0] = is_prime[1] = 0;<br>\n    for(int i=2; i*i&lt;maxn; i++)<br>\n        for(int j=i*2; j&lt;maxn;j++)<br>\n            if(is_prime[j] &amp;&amp; j%i==0)<br>\n                is_prime[j] = 0;<br>\n    //先筛出10005内的素数,is_prime[i]==1表示i为素数<br>\n    int n;<br>\n    while(scanf(\"%d\",&amp;n),n){<br>\n        int ans = 0;<br>\n        for(int i=0; i&lt;n/2; i++){//题目要求分解为不同素数，所以i不能等于n/2<br>\n            if(is_prime[i] &amp;&amp; is_prime[n-i])<br>\n                ans++;<br>\n        }<br>\n        printf(\"%d\\n\",ans);<br>\n    }<br>\n    return 0;<br>\n}</p>\n\n<pre><code>\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:46','2017-02-12 12:11:46'),(707,259,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://www.2cto.com/kf/201504/395068.html\">http://www.2cto.com/kf/201504/395068.html</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:46','2017-02-12 12:11:46'),(708,259,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>题目中的函数有很多重复运算，比如gcd(2,3), gcd(3,2)<br>\n可以优化为</p>\n\n<pre><code>  for(int i=1; i&lt;=n; i++)\n    for(int j=i; j&lt;=n; j++)\n\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>不过时间复杂度依然是O(N^2)，估计还是超时，貌似要用到一些数学定理。。。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:46','2017-02-12 12:11:46'),(709,260,'