;html&gt;\n&lt;script language=\"JavaScript\" type=\"text/javascript\"&gt; \nfunction changeBtnable(){\n    $(\"#btn\").removeAttr(\"disabled\");\n}\nfunction changeBtndisable(){\n    $(\"#btn\").attr(\"disabled\",\"true\");\n}\nfunction checkInput(){\n    var text = $(\"#money\").val();\n    if(text==null||text==\"\"){\n        changeBtndisable();\n    }\n}\n&lt;/script&gt; \n\n&lt;script src=\"jquery-3.1.1.min.js\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;body&gt; \n&lt;div id=\"dd\"&gt;\n    &lt;input id=\"money\" onmouseleave=\"checkInput()\" oninput=\"changeBtnable()\"/&gt;\n    &lt;input id=\"btn\" disabled type=\"button\"/&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt; \n\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1821,698,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>给输入框加一些时间，当输入东西时按钮就可点。当数值删除完成的时候，按钮置灰。如果还要验证数字是否合法，你就确定的时候整个提示吧。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1822,698,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>给输入框加一些时间，当输入东西时按钮就可点。当数值删除完成的时候，按钮置灰。如果还要验证数字是否合法，你就确定的时候整个提示吧。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1823,698,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><br><a href=\"\" disabled>手动加油</a><br><a href=\"/c:if\">/c:if</a><br>\n你用c:if 判断是否为空 为空的话 你把按钮改一个颜色 不给他连接地址， 意思就是他可以点 但是没反应，  如果不为空 你在把颜色改一下 你在用事件发送请求</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1824,698,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <pre><code>    &lt;input type=\"text\" /&gt;\n        &lt;input type=\"button\" disabled=\"disabled\" value=\"水水\"&gt;\n\n            $(\"input:text\").keyup(function(){\n        if($(this).val()==\"\"){\n            $(\'input:button\').attr(\"disabled\",true);\n        }else{\n            $(\'input:button\').attr(\"disabled\",null);\n        }\n    })\n\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1825,699,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>这段代码是今天回答另外个哥们写的，拿去参考下。</p>\n\n<pre lang=\"java\"><code>  class X {\n    Y y = new Y(1);\n\n    X() {\n        System.out.println(\"X\");\n    }\n\n}\n\nclass Y {\n    Y(int i) {\n        System.out.println(\"Y\" + i);\n    }\n\n}\n\nclass Z extends X {\n    Y y = new Y(2);\n\n    Z() {\n        System.out.println(\"Z\");\n    }\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        new Z();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1826,699,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>你定义的Person()函数即构造函数是无参构造函数，并且你的成员变量没有初始化。需要定义有参构造函数即可</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1827,699,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>看你的编译器了，有的会自动初始化基础类型数据</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1828,700,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>在while(){}的后面加一句sentence[i]=\'\\0\';就可以了。。。。。。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1829,700,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>0-100，应该是你下标的问题吧。数组下标检查一下，逻辑对不对</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1830,700,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>感觉i的值应该从长度减一开始，零结束</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1831,700,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>假设你一共输入了5个字母，strlen(sentence)不包括结尾的空字符，返回值就是5，也就是i被赋值为5，接下来你访问的sentence[i] 其实是数组的第6个字符。从这里就出错了。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1832,700,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>#include＜stdio.h＞<br>\n#include＜string.h＞<br>\n#define SENTENCE_SIZE 100<br>\nint main()<br>\n{<br>\n    char sentence[SENTENCE_SIZE];<br>\n    char ch;<br>\n    int i=0;<br>\n    printf(\"Enter a message:\");<br>\n    while ((ch=getchar())!=\'\\n\')<br>\n    {<br>\n        sentence[i++]=ch;<br>\n        if (i==SENTENCE_SIZE)<br>\n             break;<br>\n    }<br>\n    sentence[i]=\'\\0\';<br>\n    printf(\"Reversal is:\");<br>\n    for (i=strlen(sentence);i＞=0;i--)<br>\n        putchar (sentence[i]);<br>\n    return 0;<br>\n}</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1833,701,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/kuangbin/archive/2012/08/17/2644685.html\">http://www.cnblogs.com/kuangbin/archive/2012/08/17/2644685.html</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1834,701,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/link?url=hsX7uEor0aON_hBcoCYbsfvhlcYluyvYydcRYF_pF3CUIrB40Mfqtnt3Y-kBcoUd0lb8eRelz4Fo_LuP-nCnMRKdIyD0thvCkmlosAfucZ7\">http://baike.baidu.com/link?url=hsX7uEor0aON_hBcoCYbsfvhlcYluyvYydcRYF_pF3CUIrB40Mfqtnt3Y-kBcoUd0lb8eRelz4Fo_LuP-nCnMRKdIyD0thvCkmlosAfucZ7</a></p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1835,702,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <pre><code> 开始日期：WdatePicker({dateFmt:\'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\',maxDate:\'#F{$dp.$D(\\\'endTime\\\')}\'})\n 结束日期：WdatePicker({dateFmt:\'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\',minDate:\'#F{$dp.$D(\\\'startTime\\\')}\'})\n</code></pre>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1836,702,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>在选择时间上边加一个事件来比较开始时间和结束时间的比较  然后使用alert提醒<br>\nfunction tab(date1,date2){<br>\n    var oDate1 = new Date(date1);<br>\n    var oDate2 = new Date(date2);<br>\n    if(oDate1.getTime() &gt; oDate2.getTime()){<br>\n        console.log(\'第一个大\');<br>\n    } else {<br>\n        console.log(\'第二个大\');<br>\n    }<br>\n}</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1837,703,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>李昊阳同学，我估计问题可能有以下几种情况，你在本地连接应该可以吧，那就是线上配置问题<br>\n1：数据库相关服务没启动<br>\n2：权限问题<br>\n3：配置文件连接字符串不对</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1838,703,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>很可能是iis服务器无权访问数据库服务器；或者iis服务的启动用户无权登录数据库。</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1839,703,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p>按vs的时候应该会默认装数据库，你可以找找，或者直接在vs里找找你的数据库在哪</p>\n  </div>',1,1,0,'2017-02-12 12:13:06','2017-02-12 12:13:06'),(1840,703,'<div style=\"margin: 0 20px 10px;font-size: 14px;color: #666;line-height: 24px;word-break: break-all;word-wrap: break-word;\">\n    <p><a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201701/12/1484203640_821439.jpg