from L to R in some order. He can only visit one girl every time he goes into a classroom,otherwise the girls may fight with each other(-_-!).And he can visit the class in any order.<br>\nHere comes the problem,(NPY doesn\'t want to learn how to use excavator),he wonders how many different ways there can be in which he can visit his girls.The different ways are different means he visits these classrooms in different order.</p>\n\n<p>Input<br>\nThe first line contains the number of test cases T(1≤T≤10).<br>\nFor each test case,there are two integers n,m(0&lt;n,m≤30000) in the first line.N is the number of girls,and M is the number of times that NPY want to visit his girls.<br>\nThe following single line contains N integers, a1,a2,a3,…,an, which indicates the class number of each girl. (0&lt;ai≤30000)<br>\nThe following m lines,each line contains two integers l,r(1≤l≤r≤n),which indicates the interval NPY wants to visit.</p>\n\n<p>Output<br>\nFor each visit,print how many ways can NPY visit his girls.Because the ans may be too large,print the ans mod 1000000007.</p>\n\n<p>Sample Input<br>\n2<br>\n4 2<br>\n1 2 1 3<br>\n1 3<br>\n1 4<br>\n1 1<br>\n1<br>\n1 1</p>\n\n<p>Sample Output<br>\n3<br>\n12<br>\n1</p>\n        </dd>',0,0,'2017-02-12 12:11:39','2017-02-12 12:11:39'),(214,'http://ask.csdn.net/questions/361330','wordpress主题背景图片失效，无法显示，所有主题都不行，同时后台部分css无法显示',1,'<dd>\n          <p>下图是首页，无法显示主题背景图片<br><a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201701/30/1485758051_513681.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201701/30/1485758051_513681.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<p>按照道理应该是下面第一张图片的样子<br><a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201701/30/1485758112_638966.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201701/30/1485758112_638966.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<p>同时在后台的部分css样式无法显示<br><a href=\"http://img.ask.csdn.net/upload/201701/30/1485758172_61122.png\" target=\"_blank\"><